        <li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(0);">金沙线上娱乐是什么？</a><span id="answerspan0" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">请参阅主页</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt" lang="EN-US">&quot;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">关于我们</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt" lang="EN-US">&quot;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">。</span></span></li>
        <li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(1);">在贵公司投注安全吗？</a><span id="answerspan1" class="answerspan">我们以强大的技术力量与严格的安全管理作后盾，为您提供安全的博彩环境。除非得到客户的同意，或者法律要求，否则，我们将不会透露客户资料给第三方；若是特例，我们保留权利。此外，我们亦要求有交易往来的银行，信用卡中转代理等严格保密客户的资料。所有的存款将视为贸易户口，并不会随意公开交易信息。全部用户提供的个人资料，都通过安全的输送管道（SSL 128 位元加密标准）传送，并且储存在外界无法入侵而安全的操作系统。</span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(2);">网上博彩是否合法？</a><span id="answerspan2" class="answerspan">有的国家或地区当地法律禁止博彩，在这种情况下，请您务必遵守当地法律，如有任何疑问，请寻求当地法律部门的意见。本公司不能亦不会接受任何人士违犯当地法律所引致之任何责任。</span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(3);">我是否要交博彩税？</a><span id="answerspan3" class="answerspan">在金沙线上娱乐进行投注完全免税。</span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(4);">在金沙线上娱乐投注是否有年龄限制？</a><span id="answerspan4" class="answerspan">是的，投注合法年龄必须年满18岁。</span></li></ul></div><div class="blockTitle"><a name="H2"></a>存款常见问题</div><div class="content"><ul class="answer"><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(5);">我该如何存款？</a><span id="answerspan5" class="answerspan"><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">非常简单，您只需在</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">会员开户</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">页面里</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt">将所需资料填妥，同时将您注册的账号和密码登陆网站，在"会员存款"页面选择适合您的存款方式，按照提示一步步进行即可。
        存款成功就可以直接进行游戏下注。存款的银行卡必须先开通网上银行业务。</span></p></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(6);">存款有收取什么费用吗？</a><span id="answerspan6" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">完全免费，本公司将不收取任何费用。</span></span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(7);">最低存款额是多少？</a><span id="answerspan7" class="answerspan"><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">最低存款额为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">10</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">英镑</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 15</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">元美金</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 100</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">港币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 100</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">人民币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">或任何相等币值。</span></span></p></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(8);">最高存款限额是多少？</a><span id="answerspan8" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">单笔存款最高限额为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">千英镑</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">千元美金</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">万</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">千港币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">万</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">千人民币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">或任何相等币值。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">如超过，请分多笔存入<span style="mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">。</span></span></span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(9);">使用西联汇款时的手续费是否由客户承担？</a><span id="answerspan9" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">所有存款超过</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">200</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">元美金或相等货币的西联汇款存款，本公司将会承担其手续费用；在低于该数额的存款客户必须自己承担有关手续费。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(10);">使用信用卡存款是否要进行验证？</a><span id="answerspan10" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">是的，在使用信用卡进行存款前都必须先通过信用卡验证。在没有验证下进行的信用卡存款资金将会自动被冻结，无法进行投注或提款。金沙线上娱乐将不承担任何责任。资金必须在验证后才会解冻。</span></span></li></ul></div><div class="blockTitle"><a name="H3"></a>提款常见问题</div><div class="content"><ul class="answer"><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(11);">我该如何提款？</a><span id="answerspan11" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">非常简单，您只需
        登陆网站，在</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">会员提款</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">页面里选择适合您的提款方式，然后把提款表格填妥即可。</span><br/></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(12);">提款需要多久？</a><span id="answerspan12" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">到账时间将视您的开户银行所决定，在公司财务审核成功后，建设银行一般5-15分钟内可到账</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">，其它银行一般会在30分钟内到账。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(13);">提款需要收取手续费吗？</a><span id="answerspan13" class="answerspan">完全免费，本公司将不收取任何费用。</span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(14);">提款有上/下限吗？</a><span id="answerspan14" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">最高提款上限为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">99</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">万人民币，最低提款额为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">50</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">英镑</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 75</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">元美金</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 500</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">港币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"> / 500</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">人民币</span> <span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">或任何相等币值。</span></span></li></ul></div><div class="blockTitle"><a name="H4"></a>投注常见问题</div><div class="content"><ul class="answer"><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(15);">最低投注额是多少？</a><span id="answerspan15" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">最低投注额为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">英镑，或</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">10</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">美元，或港币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">/</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">人民币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">50</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">元。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(16);">最高投注额是多少？</a><span id="answerspan16" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">请登录后点击"会员资料"对照所显示的单注限额以及单场限额。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(17);">投注过关是否有最高派彩上限？</a><span id="answerspan17" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">单注最高派彩金额为美金</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">6</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">万元，港币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">/</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">人民币</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">50</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">万元。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(18);">网页所显示的赔率是否已经包括本金？</a><span id="answerspan18" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">港式赔率为目前亚洲市场流行的玩法赔率，赔率包含本金，英式赔率即欧洲赔率</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">,</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">赔率不包含本金。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(19);">在投注足球比赛时，如遇到比赛场地已经由主客场改为中立场，已进行的投注是否有效？</a><span id="answerspan19" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">是的，所有投注将被视为投注有效。如遇到比赛场地已经由主客场改为中立场，本公司将会以公告形式通知客户。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(20);">在投注足球比赛时，如遇到加时，加时成绩是否计算？</a><span id="answerspan20" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">除本公司事先申明，所有足球赛结果均以法定的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">90</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">分钟比分为准（包括伤停补时），加时及以<st1:chmetcnv w:st="on" tcsc="1" numbertype="3" negative="False" hasspace="False" sourcevalue="12" unitname="码">十二码</st1:chmetcnv>为决胜的结果不作为结算依据。如果仲裁机构事后改判结果，均不作为结算依据。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(21);">在投注篮球比赛时，如遇到加时，加时成绩是否计算？</a><span id="answerspan21" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">NBA</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">以及</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">WNBA</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">比赛结果以全场比分（包括加时赛）为结算依据。如果仲裁机构事后改判结果，均不作为结算依据。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(22);">投注过关是否有最多场次限制？</a><span id="answerspan22" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">目前我们提供的足球最高过关场次为七关。篮球混合过关及独赢过关最多可混十场。</span></span></li></ul></div><div class="blockTitle"><a name="H7"></a>帐户常见问题</div><div class="content"><ul class="answer">
