R-SA">会员资料</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">页面</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">修改资料</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">中的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">修改联系资料</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">即可。</span></span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(26);">为什么我用计算器把帐目一笔笔加起来后比总账多2分钱？</a><span id="answerspan26" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">因为小数点后</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">4</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">舍</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">入，这样重复多次后有时多几分钱，有时会少几分钱。</span></span></li></ul></div><div class="blockTitle"><a name="H50"></a>技术常见问题</div><div class="content"><ul class="answer"><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(27);">最低的系统配置要求是什么？</a><span id="answerspan27" class="answerspan">我们设计的网页将会提供新一代浏览器服务，提供更好的特点，让您能够享有更好的投注乐趣。我们希望您能使用Internet Explorer 5.0或者是以上的浏览器版本。</span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(28);">为什么有时赔率转换时无法正常显示变动？</a><span id="answerspan28" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">这是可能您的机器已经安装一些盗版软件因缺少系统软件，所以会出现上述情况，请重新升级您的系统。</span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(29);">为什么会显示"帐户搁置时间过长"？</a><span id="answerspan29" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">如果您在投注时遇到投注时限已过，或者是不确定有关的投注是否已经处理，您可以进入帐户内的下注状况查询投注记录或者是联络客户服务部职员确定有关的投注。请记住当您在一定的时间内没有使用有关的网页，那么有关的网页将不再活跃，并且无法浏览最新的页面，在此您必需重新登入。这是网页的保安程序之一。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体"> </span></span></li><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(30);">为什么需要清除网页快取？</a><span id="answerspan30" class="answerspan"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><br/>
<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">如果您无法浏览新的网页或者是最新的页面，并且发现所浏览的是相同或者是旧的页面，这表示您的记忆体已经满载。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">IE</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">以及</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">Netscape</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">的经常使用将导致记忆体的储存，要解决这个问题，只需依照以下的步骤：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
INTERNET EXPLORER 5.0</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">或者是以上的浏览器版本</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"><br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">在您的桌面浏览器，使用滑鼠右击。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">点击</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> &quot;Internet</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">属性</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">&quot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">再按</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">&quot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">删除文件</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">&quot; </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">中的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> &quot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">删除所有脱机内容</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">&quot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">键。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">关闭浏览器，重新启动</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">IE</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">浏览器。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">这将会清除记忆体快取，并不会清除</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">Cookies</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">或者是重要程式档案。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"><br/><br/>
NETSCAPE <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">进入电脑中的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">C-Drive</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"> </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">在此，启动程式档案。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">接着启动</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">Nestcape</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">档案</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">-</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">用户档案</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">-</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">缺省档案。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">在此，您必需寻找记忆体档案。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">启动并且取消所有的档案。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">您将会收到一个或者多个档案是无法删除，接受</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">(i.e.</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">保留</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US">) </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">这个档案，接着继续删除剩余部分。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"> <br/><br/>
</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">关闭有关的浏览器，接着再重新启动。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><br/>
</span></span></span></li></ul></div><div class="blockTitle"><a name="H51"></a>如何联络我们?</div><div class="content"><ul class="answer"><li><a href="#" onClick="return showanswer(31);">如何联络我们?</a><span id="answerspan31" class="answerspan">参阅主页"客服中心"</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div>
